  [2]: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/17/docs/api/java.base/java/lang/AutoCloseable.html
  [3]: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/essential/exceptions/tryResourceClose.html
  [4]: https://openjdk.org/jeps/378

